<h2 id="4deleting-a-file">4.Deleting a file</h2>

<p>Once again, tell the server what you want to do (delete a file), using <strong>WebRequestMethods</strong>:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-csharp" data-lang="csharp"><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="n">ftpRequest</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Method</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="n">WebRequestMethods</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Ftp</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">DeleteFile</span><span class="p">;</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></figure>

<p>And thatâ€™s all ! - no additional code is required to do this.<br />
